(225, 1, '2016-04-03 03:39:40', '2016-04-02 23:39:40', 'Враховуючи індивідуальні особливості замовника (унікальний бізнес-процес, відсутність галузевої конфігурації у сфері діяльності замовника тощо), наша компанія може суттєво підвищити ефективність інформаційної системи. Ми здійснюємо доопрацювання програмних продуктів 1С, враховуючи Ваші вимоги та специфіку діяльності.\n<ul>\nДо даної категорії послуг можна віднести:\n	<li>доопрацювання друкованих форм та звітів;</li>\n	<li>зміна прав користувачів;</li>\n	<li>розроблення нових довідників та документів;</li>\n	<li>автоматизація певних дій та процедур;</li>\n<li>інші.</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n\n \n\n \n\nДоработки 1CНаиболее частые доработки 1С:\n\n    Доработка печатных форм;\n    Доработка отчетов;\n    Изменение прав пользователей;\n    Разработка обработок для автоматизации каких-либо действий и процедур;\n    Разработка новых справочников и документов;\n\nСтоимость доработок 1С зависит от объемов потраченного времени на работы.', 'Додаткові корективи в 1С', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '207-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-04-03 03:39:40', '2016-04-02 23:39:40', '', 207, 'http://apple3/index.php/2016/03/08/207-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(226, 1, '2016-03-08 00:47:39', '2016-03-07 20:47:39', '<img class=" wp-image-203 aligncenter" src="http://apple3/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Classic-Home_07-300x144.png" alt="Classic---Home_07" width="652" height="313" />\r\n<p class="none">The iPad mini is the newly introduced member of the “i” family. Pixeden has done a phenomenal job of replicating iPad Mini into a\r\nvector form and has made it freely available for everyone to use. A second version of the iPhone 5 mockup template released by\r\nPixeden, which is the couterpart to the originally released black version. This template also includes high quality background floor\r\ntextures.</p>\r\n<a class="read-more" href="http://apple3/index.php/2016/03/07/year-in-review-our-favourite-apps-from-2012/"> Read more</a>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<p class="none">Looking to showcase your latest Android based mobile application? Author, Ondrej Lechan, designed three highly detailed and\r\ncustomizable HTC branded phone mockups to meet that specific need. The HTC One X, S, and V series phones can be the perfect\r\nsidekick to showcase your mobile design work. Looking to showcase your latest Android based mobile application?</p>\r\n<p class="none">Author, Ondrej Lechan, designed three highly detailed and customizable HTC branded phone mockups to meet that specific need.</p>\r\n<p class="none">Intent is a unique PSD template that’s ideal for design agencies and design professionals to illustrate their portfolio. A fantastic replica\r\nof the 13” MacBook Air by Koy Carraway. This is a fully layered &amp; scalable MacBook Air made almost entirely from vector shapes in\r\nPhotoshop.</p>\r\n<img class=" wp-image-202 aligncenter" src="http://apple3/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Classic-Home_03-300x219.png" alt="Classic---Home_03" width="540" height="394" />\r\n<h3>Features of Wunderlist</h3>\r\n<p class="none">Looking to showcase your latest Android based mobile application? Author, Ondrej Lechan, designed three highly detailed and\r\ncustomizable HTC branded phone mockups to meet that specific need. The HTC One X, S, and V series phones can be the perfect\r\nsidekick to showcase your mobile design work. Looking to showcase your latest Android based mobile application?</p>\r\n<p class="none">Author, Ondrej Lechan, designed three highly detailed and customizable HTC branded phone mockups to meet that specific need.</p>\r\n<img class=" wp-image-198 aligncenter" src="http://apple3/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Classic-Blog_11-300x171.png" alt="Classic---Blog_11" width="519" height="296" />\r\n<p class="none">Looking to showcase your latest Android based mobile application? Author, Ondrej Lechan, designed three highly detailed and\r\ncustomizable HTC branded phone mockups to meet that specific need. The HTC One X, S, and V series phones can be the perfect\r\nsidekick to showcase your mobile design work. Looking to showcase your latest Android based mobile application?</p>', 'Year in Review: Our Favourite Apps  from 2012', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '207-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-08 00:47:39', '2016-03-07 20:47:39', '', 207, 'http://apple3/index.php/2016/03/08/207-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
